All Classes

Class Description
CredentialsNotFoundException
CredentialsNotFoundException is an unchecked exception thrown when an attempt to obtain or use credentials fails because they do not exist.
HostManager
The HostManager provides access to the implementation of the IHostManager interface.
IHostManager
Manager for retrieving hosts defined in the Topaz Workbench client.
ZOSUIUserCredentialsManager
This manager is used to connect a Topaz Workbench UI user to a z/OS host configured in the Topaz Workbench client and to retrieve their credentials for connecting to a z/OS host with the Topaz API.
